<MudText Typo="Typo.h3" GutterBottom="true" Align="Align.Start">System Overview</MudText>
<MudText Class="mb-8" Align="Align.Justify">This system's primary objective is to seamlessly incorporate OpenAI GPT for generating 
    responses in accordance with user prompts. Furthermore, it possesses the capability to analyze, process, 
    and extract content from PDF documents, adapting prompts dynamically to fit the context. The user interface 
    has been designed to simplify the entry of diverse queries in prompt format, with the resulting responses 
    from OpenAI GPT presented in an organized and easily readable layout. Additionally, the system is enriched 
    with extensively trained communication skills, guaranteeing accurate and contextually fitting AI responses.</MudText>

